            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-12-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="201" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d201">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Department of State, on July 23, released two statements by Secretary
                    Marshall dealing with the fighting in northwestern Greece and with the question
                    of an international brigade; for texts, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, August 3, 1947, page 228.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
